            <h1 class="page-header">Welcome to SimplePHPSite</h1>

            <p>This is the default installation for SimplePHPSite.</p>

            <p>Things to do now:</p>

            <ul>
              <li>adjust configuration settings in <code>includes/config.php</code> either by hand or using <a href="admin.php">admin.php</a></li>
              <li><font color="red">delete  <code>admin.php</code> and <code>includes/admin.php</code>!</font></li>
              <li>replace the content of the <code>pages/index</code> file with your home page content</li>
              <li>edit the navigation links in <code>includes/navigation.php</code></li>
              <li>add custom CSS to <code>css/custom.css</code></li>
              <li>replace the <code>images/splash.jpg</code> file with your own background image</li>
            </ul>
